  "texts": [
    "In the top, we see GPT-3.5's guardrail blocks the original query.",
    "Meanwhile, at the bottom, the PAP elicits harmful content with links to real websites.",
    "We redact the sensitive information.",
    "Llama-2 7b Chat (Touvron et al., 2023), GPT-3.5 (gpt-3.5-0613), GPT-4 (gpt-4-0613) (OpenAI, 2023), Claude 1 (claude-instant-v1), and Claude 2 (claude-v2) (Anthropic, 2023).",
    "We chose these models as they are the most accessible and widely used modern LLMs, likely to be deployed or interacted with large amounts of everyday users."
